It's my own darn fault.

00:20:53.832 --> 00:20:57.965
Oh, put your arms around me and come along, okay?

00:20:57.965 --> 00:20:59.999
- Jeez.
- Yeah, yeah.

00:20:59.999 --> 00:21:02.532
- Oh, my.
- Oh, dear.

00:21:04.965 --> 00:21:08.665
From what I heard,
she seems to be a slave who fled Hanyang.

00:21:08.665 --> 00:21:09.932
A slave?

00:21:09.932 --> 00:21:13.999
It appears she's caught in serious trouble.

00:21:13.999 --> 00:21:16.199
It's quite troubling.

00:21:17.199 --> 00:21:19.699
But why are you going there?

00:21:19.699 --> 00:21:22.632
Because I took on a certain role.

00:21:22.632 --> 00:21:26.799
Like a debt collector scarier than tigers.

00:21:31.732 --> 00:21:34.632
Is it possible that the Crown Princess didn't die

00:21:34.632 --> 00:21:37.384
and was sold into servitude as a palace slave?

00:21:38.699 --> 00:21:43.599
The body decayed in water too long,
so I couldn't verify the face properly.

00:21:43.599 --> 00:21:46.365
Even on the slightest chance...

00:21:46.365 --> 00:21:48.799
Your Highness couldn't protect her,

00:21:48.799 --> 00:21:51.765
so who else would have guarded Her Highness?

00:21:54.632 --> 00:21:57.332
My apologies.

00:21:57.332 --> 00:22:01.099
Your Highness, that porter
can't possibly be Her Highness.

00:22:01.099 --> 00:22:03.032
If she truly were Her Highness,

00:22:03.032 --> 00:22:06.999
she'd be a traitor who refused
the royal poison and fled.

00:22:06.999 --> 00:22:08.765
That makes her a grave criminal.

00:22:08.765 --> 00:22:12.065
If that girl really is her,

00:22:12.065 --> 00:22:14.632
if only she's still alive...

00:22:14.632 --> 00:22:17.032
I just want to grab that hand and run away.

00:22:18.399 --> 00:22:21.096
But if that girl isn't my lady,

00:22:21.765 --> 00:22:25.416
if she's truly just a porter or a runaway slave,

00:22:27.299 --> 00:22:29.384
that girl will die.

00:22:30.399 --> 00:22:32.552
So let's say

00:22:35.099 --> 00:22:37.499
I pity her.

00:23:14.465 --> 00:23:17.032
May I ask you something?

00:23:17.032 --> 00:23:19.599
I heard there's a five-day market here.
Why can't I see it?

00:23:19.599 --> 00:23:21.665
Oh, what a madman.

00:23:21.665 --> 00:23:22.665
It's Hye hour now.

00:23:22.665 --> 00:23:24.565
How could the market be open?

00:23:24.565 --> 00:23:25.565
Oh, for heaven's sake.

00:23:25.565 --> 00:23:27.732
Oh, no, it's ruined! Oh, no!

00:23:27.732 --> 00:23:28.932
I just arrived here.

00:23:28.932 --> 00:23:31.265
Why are they closing so early?

00:23:31.265 --> 00:23:33.165
Today's business is ruined, completely ruined.

00:23:33.165 --> 00:23:35.165
Even customers need to sleep, you know.

00:23:35.165 --> 00:23:36.765
You should leave now. I'm busy.

00:23:36.765 --> 00:23:38.765
Oh, really.

00:23:39.599 --> 00:23:41.699
Huh? Where'd she go?

00:23:41.699 --> 00:23:44.232
You seem busy. Get back to work.

00:23:44.232 --> 00:23:46.465
- What do we do?
- Where did she go?

00:23:46.465 --> 00:23:48.532
Let's go that way.

00:24:00.865 --> 00:24:02.665
Oink oink.

00:24:06.465 --> 00:24:08.399
[At Hye hour, behind Eunwolgak, pretend to
have decided to take your own life, and come out.]

00:24:08.399 --> 00:24:11.932
At Hye hour, behind Eunwolgak,

00:24:11.932 --> 00:24:14.732
pretend to have decided
to take your own life, and come out.

00:24:35.265 --> 00:24:36.399
Why are you doing this?

00:24:36.399 --> 00:24:39.400
I need to check something. Excuse me briefly.

00:24:43.332 --> 00:24:44.932
What are you doing now...

00:24:44.932 --> 00:24:46.965
Right, the fabric merchant from earlier.

00:24:46.965 --> 00:24:50.165
Let me check the luggage on your back.

00:24:50.165 --> 00:24:51.299
What's with my luggage?

00:24:51.299 --> 00:24:52.399
What's with my luggage?

00:24:52.399 --> 00:24:53.932
Wait.

00:24:53.932 --> 00:24:55.232
Let me go.

00:24:55.232 --> 00:24:56.899
Let me go.

00:24:56.899 --> 00:24:58.365
No, no.

00:24:58.365 --> 00:24:59.932
No, why?

00:24:59.932 --> 00:25:01.765
No.

00:25:02.932 --> 00:25:04.465
- Miss.
- No.

00:25:04.465 --> 00:25:06.032
What are you doing here?

00:25:06.032 --> 00:25:08.332
I've been looking everywhere for you!

00:25:08.332 --> 00:25:10.932
Let us go.

00:25:10.932 --> 00:25:12.765
No.

00:25:14.965 --> 00:25:16.432
Run away!

00:25:16.432 --> 00:25:19.799
I'll handle things here, run away!

00:25:19.799 --> 00:25:21.932
That won't do.

00:25:21.932 --> 00:25:25.299
Our young lady has a place she must go...

00:25:27.165 --> 00:25:28.785
My lord.

00:25:37.199 --> 00:25:39.632
What brings you here, my lord?

00:25:39.632 --> 00:25:41.232
Go.

00:25:41.232 --> 00:25:43.732
How will you handle them all alone?

00:25:43.732 --> 00:25:45.499
Worry about me when you have time to spare.

00:25:45.499 --> 00:25:48.299
For now, you should listen to me.

00:25:49.265 --> 00:25:52.299
Oh, this is a secret,

00:25:52.299 --> 00:25:54.132
but truth is

00:25:56.499 --> 00:25:58.099
I'm a master of fighting.

00:25:58.099 --> 00:26:00.132
You can trust me and go.

00:26:06.999 --> 00:26:10.032
Then I'll leave it to you, my lord.

00:26:11.765 --> 00:26:13.999
My lord, though I don't know who you are...

00:26:13.999 --> 00:26:17.632
I tolerate this rudeness only
because I don't know your status.

00:26:17.632 --> 00:26:19.165
I'm late to introduce myself.

00:26:19.165 --> 00:26:21.365
I am Je Woon...

00:26:29.632 --> 00:26:33.199
His Highness orders you to no longer
involve yourself in this matter.

00:26:33.199 --> 00:26:34.865
If you intervene in the Kim family's affairs,

00:26:34.865 --> 00:26:38.129
it may be perceived as a political maneuvering.

00:26:43.699 --> 00:26:45.499
Stop.

00:26:47.699 --> 00:26:49.565
Why are you doing this? Let us go.

00:26:49.565 --> 00:26:51.432
If I let you go,

00:26:52.299 --> 00:26:53.532
where would you go?

00:26:53.532 --> 00:26:55.132
How far do you think you'll get?

00:26:55.132 --> 00:26:58.999
Even if that girl survives,
do you think you'll be safe?

00:26:58.999 --> 00:27:01.532
It doesn't matter, so step aside and leave us be.

00:27:01.532 --> 00:27:02.865
It's already too late.

00:27:02.865 --> 00:27:06.332
- Miss.
- Miss.

00:27:20.599 --> 00:27:22.499
It's all

00:27:24.499 --> 00:27:26.399
over now.

00:27:29.565 --> 00:27:32.832
No, you can't take her.

00:27:34.199 --> 00:27:37.832
You're accomplices in this too.

00:27:38.499 --> 00:27:43.165
If anything happens to the young lady,
half the blame falls on you, understand?

00:27:45.499 --> 00:27:47.965
- Escort the young lady.
- Yes.

00:27:47.965 --> 00:27:49.965
Come this way, young lady.

00:27:49.965 --> 00:27:51.132
Young lady, wait a moment.

00:27:51.132 --> 00:27:52.865
Young lady.

00:27:52.865 --> 00:27:54.632
Let me go, please.

00:27:54.632 --> 00:27:56.465
No.

00:28:08.665 --> 00:28:12.599
You're worse than them, my lord.

00:28:12.599 --> 00:28:17.199
They serve masters who hold their lives,

00:28:17.199 --> 00:28:19.665
but you are only siding with the highborn

00:28:19.665 --> 00:28:22.999
because of some ridiculous law.

00:28:25.665 --> 00:28:28.264
I heard you're a runaway slave from Hanyang.

00:28:29.365 --> 00:28:31.065
Who said such a...

00:28:31.065 --> 00:28:36.104
If you want to hide your status,
fix that thick Hanyang accent first.

00:28:36.932 --> 00:28:39.232
So,

00:28:39.232 --> 00:28:41.599
are you threatening me with my identity now?

00:28:41.599 --> 00:28:43.032
I'm not blaming you.

00:28:43.032 --> 00:28:45.672
Nor am I here to punish you.

00:28:47.199 --> 00:28:49.448
You're very lucky.

00:28:50.632 --> 00:28:53.160
Having met me with that face.

00:28:54.032 --> 00:28:56.232
I'll give you the money you wanted.

00:28:56.232 --> 00:28:59.132
So step away from this matter
and leave Hanyang immediately.

00:28:59.132 --> 00:29:01.032
Why would you give me money?

00:29:01.032 --> 00:29:03.499
Isn't that why you're acting like this,
for the money?

00:29:03.499 --> 00:29:04.932
- What is this...
- A silver dagger.

00:29:04.932 --> 00:29:07.732
The Records of Virtuous Women,
Anthology of Suicides, The Tale of Chun Hyang.

00:29:07.732 --> 00:29:09.999
- That's...
- Telling others to become chaste women.

00:29:09.999 --> 00:29:13.732
You sell all these items encouraging suicide.

00:29:13.732 --> 00:29:16.132
Don't you hate seeing women you know die?

00:29:16.132 --> 00:29:18.399
Do merchants have no scruples at all?

00:29:18.399 --> 00:29:20.565
It's for disguise.

00:29:20.565 --> 00:29:22.365
Why would I sell such things?

00:29:22.365 --> 00:29:23.465
'Such things'?

00:29:23.465 --> 00:29:25.765
If someone wants to die, you should stop them.

00:29:25.765 --> 00:29:28.499
Not praise them by publishing
some 'The Records of Virtuous Women.'

00:29:28.499 --> 00:29:31.848
If you hold a blade, stab the villain.
Why cut your own throat?

00:29:39.165 --> 00:29:40.465
What a novel interpretation.

00:29:40.465 --> 00:29:43.599
What would Chun Hyang,
the model of chastity, say to that?

00:29:43.599 --> 00:29:47.999
Oh look, another noble
who only knows Chun Hyang by name.

00:29:47.999 --> 00:29:49.665
Listen carefully.

00:29:49.665 --> 00:29:55.365
What Chun Hyang protected
wasn't chastity, but herself.

00:30:00.130 --> 00:30:03.083
[The Tale of Chun Hyang]

00:30:05.199 --> 00:30:07.099
- You enjoy that book?
- Yes.

00:30:07.099 --> 00:30:11.272
I never knew you cared
so much about chastity, my lady.

00:30:13.399 --> 00:30:16.199
Or is this some kind of signal?

00:30:16.199 --> 00:30:18.577
The content was quite indecent.

00:30:22.499 --> 00:30:26.132
Is that all you saw in The Tale of Chun Hyang?

00:30:26.132 --> 00:30:28.999
I feel like you scold me every day.

00:30:28.999 --> 00:30:31.532
What Chun Hyang tried to protect

00:30:31.532 --> 00:30:34.532
wasn't chastity, but dignity.

00:30:35.799 --> 00:30:39.565
Chastity was merely a tool.

00:30:40.532 --> 00:30:43.532
A tool to protect her own worth.

00:30:45.499 --> 00:30:47.399
A tool?

00:30:50.065 --> 00:30:52.299
It was a tool to protect herself
from Magistrate Byeon,

00:30:52.299 --> 00:30:55.532
who insisted she was a courtesan for his own lust,

00:30:55.532 --> 00:30:58.665
even though he knew she wasn't.

00:30:58.665 --> 00:31:02.888
A kind of armor against a cruel world.

00:31:03.532 --> 00:31:07.065
Where did you hear that story?

00:31:07.065 --> 00:31:10.665
I didn't hear it anywhere. It's my own thought.

00:31:10.665 --> 00:31:13.032
That can't be.

00:31:13.865 --> 00:31:17.065
Do you think we lowborn people
have no thoughts of our own?

00:31:20.165 --> 00:31:22.232
Then,

00:31:22.232 --> 00:31:25.099
do you know what happens

00:31:28.132 --> 00:31:30.499
if you catch a falling petal?

00:31:31.565 --> 00:31:34.312
If I catch a falling petal...

00:31:41.799 --> 00:31:44.049
If I catch a falling petal...

00:31:51.265 --> 00:31:54.465
Why should I tell that to you?

00:31:54.465 --> 00:31:55.899
I'll take my leave now.

00:31:55.899 --> 00:32:00.081
I don't wish to exchange words
with rude petty men like you.

00:32:04.732 --> 00:32:07.299
If I resolve this matter,

00:32:07.299 --> 00:32:09.032
will you answer me?

00:32:09.032 --> 00:32:10.032
What?

00:32:10.032 --> 00:32:12.465
If I resolve this matter,

00:32:13.232 --> 00:32:15.699
will you give me an answer?

00:32:17.432 --> 00:32:20.532
I'll take your silence as a yes.

00:32:20.532 --> 00:32:22.465
First, get treated.

00:32:22.465 --> 00:32:25.576
That wound bothers me.

00:32:33.032 --> 00:32:34.165
What are you doing?

00:32:34.165 --> 00:32:35.932
Let go. What is this?

00:32:35.932 --> 00:32:38.465
Let go of me. Why are you doing this?

00:32:38.465 --> 00:32:40.832
Why treat me like luggage?

00:32:40.832 --> 00:32:43.032
Where are you taking me?

00:32:43.032 --> 00:32:44.865
Why this? Oh, my.

00:32:44.865 --> 00:32:48.165
The treatment's all finished,
but why are you stopping me?

00:32:48.165 --> 00:32:51.332
The lord who brought you said to keep you here

00:32:51.332 --> 00:32:53.232
until he returns.

00:32:53.232 --> 00:32:55.565
I said I'm leaving.

00:32:55.565 --> 00:32:58.432
Why should I be bound by
a complete stranger's words?

00:32:58.432 --> 00:33:00.799
That's not my concern.

00:33:00.799 --> 00:33:04.265
He left without paying.

00:33:06.565 --> 00:33:09.832
Ah, money.

00:33:09.832 --> 00:33:11.865
Well, money does matter.

00:33:11.865 --> 00:33:12.932
But what should I do?

00:33:12.932 --> 00:33:16.232
Looks like you're gonna lose quite a bit of money.

00:33:16.232 --> 00:33:19.932
You look like you're gonna lose
way more money than the others.

00:33:19.932 --> 00:33:22.232
What, what does that...

00:33:22.232 --> 00:33:24.665
Why me?

00:33:26.632 --> 00:33:29.632
Want me to tell you why?

00:33:41.499 --> 00:33:43.499
Hey, you. Take it easy.

00:33:43.499 --> 00:33:45.699
Thief. There's a thief!

00:33:45.699 --> 00:33:47.565
Where?

00:33:48.968 --> 00:33:50.499
Darn it.

00:33:50.499 --> 00:33:53.299
- Where's the thief?
- Over there.

00:34:13.332 --> 00:34:17.765
Go put on a show and come back in one piece.

00:34:21.765 --> 00:34:23.565
Catch him.

00:34:35.565 --> 00:34:36.999
Hup! Hah!

00:34:36.999 --> 00:34:40.232
That's right.

00:34:47.565 --> 00:34:49.532
Serves him right.

00:34:51.399 --> 00:34:53.365
More coming from behind.

00:34:57.732 --> 00:35:01.165
A plum blossom in a place like this...

00:35:11.865 --> 00:35:13.099
Oh, you startled me.

00:35:13.099 --> 00:35:17.332
You rat! You knew I was here
and did that on purpose, right?

00:35:24.165 --> 00:35:26.165
They say you shouldn't hurt
a person even with a flower.

00:35:26.165 --> 00:35:28.832
But you've shattered everything I believed in.

00:35:28.832 --> 00:35:32.165
Had you just revealed your status,

00:35:32.165 --> 00:35:34.899
you could've kept those principles.

00:35:34.899 --> 00:35:37.499
That wouldn't have looked very cool, would it?

00:35:39.032 --> 00:35:40.499
Open the door, Shin Won.

00:35:40.499 --> 00:35:43.532
- Hey, go open it.
- Shin Won.

00:35:51.362 --> 00:35:53.432
This is serious.

00:35:53.432 --> 00:35:56.232
Everyone, gather up.

00:35:56.232 --> 00:35:59.399
Kim Ji Pyeong is trying to get a chastity monument

00:35:59.399 --> 00:36:04.165
by forcing his 15-year-old
daughter-in-law to commit suicide.

00:36:05.499 --> 00:36:08.032
That's not the issue here.

00:36:08.032 --> 00:36:11.665
If this gets exposed, the entire village
will suffer consequences.

00:36:11.665 --> 00:36:13.532
What consequences?

00:36:14.199 --> 00:36:16.932
Taxes and labor demands will skyrocket.

00:36:16.932 --> 00:36:17.932
By severalfold.

00:36:17.932 --> 00:36:20.399
That's the punishment for falsifying
the Virtuous Widow monument.

00:36:20.399 --> 00:36:22.899
The village's status will be downgraded.

00:36:22.899 --> 00:36:24.665
- Taxes?
- Labor?

00:36:24.665 --> 00:36:27.165
They'll increase them? This darn country.

00:36:27.165 --> 00:36:28.365
Exactly.

00:36:28.365 --> 00:36:30.899
So what do we do?

00:36:30.899 --> 00:36:32.765
We need to storm in right now and say,

00:36:32.765 --> 00:36:34.065
'We knew nothing!'

00:36:34.065 --> 00:36:38.999
Show them we're innocent citizens
who came to save his daughter-in-law.

00:36:38.999 --> 00:36:42.999
Are we going to take the blame
all because of that man?

00:36:42.999 --> 00:36:44.932
Then there's no time to stand here.

00:36:44.932 --> 00:36:48.165
Let's go finish off that punk immediately.

00:36:48.165 --> 00:36:53.165
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

00:36:53.999 --> 00:36:57.736
Go honorably as the daughter-in-law
of the Kim family.

00:36:58.599 --> 00:37:00.765
I made a promise to my husband.

00:37:00.765 --> 00:37:03.899
I vowed never to follow him in death.

00:37:03.899 --> 00:37:06.765
We promised to meet again long from now

00:37:06.765 --> 00:37:09.199
and live together for a hundred years.

00:37:09.199 --> 00:37:12.765
Who would benefit from a death
that neither my husband

00:37:12.765 --> 00:37:14.399
nor I wished for?

00:37:14.399 --> 00:37:17.832
How dare you beg for your life
by selling my late son's honor?

00:37:17.832 --> 00:37:20.632
A will can always be forged, and as for a life,

00:37:20.632 --> 00:37:22.232
well, I could always end it myself...

00:37:22.232 --> 00:37:23.332
No, that won't do.

00:37:23.332 --> 00:37:25.532
Right, that won't do.

00:37:27.199 --> 00:37:29.632
Who are you?

00:37:29.632 --> 00:37:32.265
You, sir...

00:37:32.265 --> 00:37:34.132
Let me see.

00:37:34.132 --> 00:37:36.432
A silver dagger for slitting throats,

00:37:36.432 --> 00:37:38.032
a rope for hanging,

00:37:38.032 --> 00:37:41.465
and the water used for poisoning...

00:37:41.465 --> 00:37:42.999
It's obvious, isn't it?

00:37:42.999 --> 00:37:44.365
Who are you?

00:37:44.365 --> 00:37:46.032
How did you get in here?

00:37:46.032 --> 00:37:49.132
Is there no one outside?

00:37:52.699 --> 00:37:55.632
Now, abandon any thought of killing that woman.

00:37:55.632 --> 00:37:58.565
If I hear even a whisper that she's dead,

00:37:58.565 --> 00:38:03.165
not even three generations of your family
could take the civil service exam.

00:38:03.165 --> 00:38:05.632
If that woman dies,

00:38:05.632 --> 00:38:07.665
so will you.

00:38:10.665 --> 00:38:12.299
- Open the door.
- Who's there?

00:38:12.299 --> 00:38:15.199
- Who is it?
- You miserable punk!

00:38:15.199 --> 00:38:17.960
- Open up!
- Who's there?

00:38:17.960 --> 00:38:19.165
Wait, wait...

00:38:19.165 --> 00:38:20.776
Hey, you!

00:38:20.776 --> 00:38:23.934
- You...
- Why is he tied up?

00:38:24.932 --> 00:38:28.365
That wretch Kim Ji Pyeong got what he deserved.

00:38:36.032 --> 00:38:37.865
Young lady.

00:38:40.865 --> 00:38:42.032
What a relief.

00:38:42.032 --> 00:38:44.299
Are you unharmed?

00:38:45.132 --> 00:38:46.565
What's going on here?

00:38:46.565 --> 00:38:47.599
It's unusual.

00:38:47.599 --> 00:38:49.232
It's a misunderstanding, right?

00:38:49.232 --> 00:38:51.165
It really does seem so.

00:38:51.165 --> 00:38:54.565
If you return to the palace
without arresting him, they'll kill us.

00:38:54.565 --> 00:38:57.399
Then let's just smile for now.

00:38:57.399 --> 00:39:00.199
Over there, over there!

00:39:00.932 --> 00:39:03.565
That's him!

00:39:03.565 --> 00:39:06.232
My lord!

00:39:10.399 --> 00:39:11.999
What's the matter?

00:39:11.999 --> 00:39:14.165
We received a report of a thief
and came to investigate.

00:39:14.165 --> 00:39:15.265
No.

00:39:15.265 --> 00:39:17.865
They tried to force this lady
to kill herself for the monument,

00:39:17.865 --> 00:39:21.299
but this gentleman here saved her.

00:39:21.299 --> 00:39:23.665
Is that true?

00:39:23.665 --> 00:39:26.376
Oh, well...

00:39:26.376 --> 00:39:29.165
The woman speaks the truth.

00:39:29.165 --> 00:39:32.099
I witnessed the scene myself.

00:39:33.099 --> 00:39:34.465
Arrest that criminal

00:39:34.465 --> 00:39:38.199
who defied the law and insulted His Majesty!

00:39:38.199 --> 00:39:40.399
Arrest him!

00:39:40.399 --> 00:39:41.765
Quickly, take him away.

00:39:41.765 --> 00:39:43.999
By the way, who are you?

00:39:43.999 --> 00:39:47.732
Ah, this person is the Crown Prince...

00:39:49.532 --> 00:39:55.499
Crown Prince specially appointed
him as a secret inspector.

00:39:57.032 --> 00:39:59.332
Show us your royal token.

00:40:05.299 --> 00:40:08.765
Are you Shin Won?

00:40:08.765 --> 00:40:10.565
Then, he's...

00:40:12.065 --> 00:40:14.599
- Your Highness.
- His Highness personally

00:40:14.599 --> 00:40:18.665
appointed him as the secret inspector.

00:40:18.665 --> 00:40:20.032
He's the secret inspector.

00:40:20.032 --> 00:40:22.399
His... Highness.

00:40:24.499 --> 00:40:27.399
Yes, my lord, I shall obey your orders.

00:40:27.399 --> 00:40:30.165
Good.

00:40:30.165 --> 00:40:31.499
Arrest the criminals.

00:40:31.499 --> 00:40:33.299
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:40:35.332 --> 00:40:36.932
It's over now.

00:40:36.932 --> 00:40:38.932
Don't worry.

00:40:43.732 --> 00:40:45.932
You vile wretch.

00:40:59.699 --> 00:41:02.532
Will you answer me now?

00:41:02.532 --> 00:41:06.732
Do you know what happens
if you catch a falling petal?

00:41:14.132 --> 00:41:15.765
Did you know that?

00:41:15.765 --> 00:41:18.632
If you catch a falling petal,

00:41:18.632 --> 00:41:21.132
your first love will come true.

00:41:45.599 --> 00:41:47.165
Why? Why?

00:41:47.165 --> 00:41:49.399
You said you didn't know,
but why keep following me?

00:41:49.399 --> 00:41:51.272
When did I ever say I didn't know?

00:41:51.272 --> 00:41:52.999
I just said you'd become the person
who caught the petal.

00:41:52.999 --> 00:41:55.532
So that means you don't understand.

00:41:55.532 --> 00:41:57.532
Since my business with you is concluded,

00:41:57.532 --> 00:41:59.632
you should leave now.

00:42:01.199 --> 00:42:05.064
But I still have unfinished business.

00:42:11.632 --> 00:42:13.999
Thank you

00:42:13.999 --> 00:42:16.332
for saving the young lady.

00:42:21.665 --> 00:42:24.065
No need for gratitude.

00:42:24.065 --> 00:42:26.184
I did it for my own sake anyway.

00:42:27.165 --> 00:42:29.132
To be precise, what I saved

00:42:29.132 --> 00:42:31.532
was that woman's late husband.

00:42:31.532 --> 00:42:34.265
If he knew she died like that,

00:42:34.265 --> 00:42:36.616
he'd wander the afterlife endlessly.

00:42:37.632 --> 00:42:39.793
This was done

00:42:39.793 --> 00:42:41.832
for a weak man

00:42:44.865 --> 00:42:47.528
who would regret it for a long time.

00:44:08.065 --> 00:44:13.199
My apologies. You looked so distressed, my lord...

00:44:14.199 --> 00:44:15.899
Was that supposed to comfort me?

00:44:15.899 --> 00:44:17.532
What right do I have to do that?

00:44:17.532 --> 00:44:20.199
What connection could there be
between your sorrow and me?

00:44:20.199 --> 00:44:22.265
There is a connection.

00:44:26.165 --> 00:44:28.899
Because of you, I've been

00:44:29.699 --> 00:44:31.699
trapped in a dream.

00:44:34.999 --> 00:44:37.932
A long-awaited

00:44:37.932 --> 00:44:39.832
nightmare.

00:44:44.565 --> 00:44:48.032
You look sorrowful even now.

00:44:48.032 --> 00:44:50.199
Then this time,

00:44:50.865 --> 00:44:53.465
how will you comfort me?

00:45:00.232 --> 00:45:02.899
Shall I buy you some soup rice?

00:45:02.899 --> 00:45:04.999
- So random?
- A full stomach

00:45:04.999 --> 00:45:07.299
warms the heart.

00:45:07.299 --> 00:45:09.432
It's not a bad idea.

00:45:13.132 --> 00:45:14.332
My lord.

00:45:14.332 --> 00:45:16.432
It's getting late, so you should return now...

00:45:16.432 --> 00:45:17.565
Very well.

00:45:17.565 --> 00:45:20.712
Buy me the soup rice.

00:45:23.499 --> 00:45:27.165
His Highness resolved the false chaste widow case?

00:45:27.165 --> 00:45:29.599
Did he want to imitate a sage king or something?

00:45:29.599 --> 00:45:31.965
Oh, hardly.

00:45:31.965 --> 00:45:33.432
He just stumbled into it.

00:45:33.432 --> 00:45:37.865
Even if indulgent, the Crown Prince
who cares nothing for politics,

00:45:37.865 --> 00:45:40.165
what kind of sage king...

00:45:42.065 --> 00:45:45.099
Whether stumbled upon or hunted down,

00:45:45.099 --> 00:45:48.865
a rampaging tiger needs a collar.

00:45:48.865 --> 00:45:50.899
Is Tak here?

00:45:50.899 --> 00:45:53.365
Yes, what can I do?

00:45:53.365 --> 00:45:57.099
It's been ages since you sent a letter
to Woo Hee, and she still hasn't come?

00:45:57.099 --> 00:46:00.832
The young lady remains stubbornly resistant.

00:46:01.665 --> 00:46:04.232
Send a palanquin immediately.

00:46:04.232 --> 00:46:06.732
Drag her here if necessary.

00:46:36.065 --> 00:46:40.299
You must enter royal marriage
with the Crown Prince. Come to the capital.

00:46:40.299 --> 00:46:42.232
If you refuse again this time,

00:46:42.232 --> 00:46:47.232
your father will burn down Sinjusa.

00:46:47.232 --> 00:46:50.999
We just need to buy up all the poison
in Yeongdeok and fetch water for it.

00:46:50.999 --> 00:46:52.199
What's the problem?

00:46:52.199 --> 00:46:56.265
Ah, this father-daughter feud
will boost the local economy.

00:46:58.699 --> 00:47:03.299
So you have no intention of marrying into royalty?

00:47:03.299 --> 00:47:05.632
My lady.

00:47:05.632 --> 00:47:08.932
You're already past marriageable age.

00:47:08.932 --> 00:47:13.632
Do you intend to grow old and die alone
as a solitary maiden ghost?

00:47:13.632 --> 00:47:16.499
- Not at all.
- But how long can you hold out?

00:47:16.499 --> 00:47:19.865
Do you think you can marry your true love?

00:47:31.932 --> 00:47:35.211
[One Year Ago]

00:47:56.432 --> 00:47:58.899
Would you like to try?

00:48:01.065 --> 00:48:02.732
I don't feel inclined to.

00:48:02.732 --> 00:48:04.799
Isn't it a tool to harm people?

00:48:04.799 --> 00:48:06.532
No, it's a tool to protect.

00:48:06.532 --> 00:48:10.232
If I fire this at someone,

00:48:10.232 --> 00:48:13.032
it's to protect something.

00:48:24.665 --> 00:48:26.899
Don't use this gun.

00:48:28.465 --> 00:48:31.199
I'll always

00:48:31.199 --> 00:48:33.999
hold your hand whenever you need me.

00:48:48.632 --> 00:48:50.769
Then I must

00:48:50.769 --> 00:48:53.399
protect him now.

00:49:20.365 --> 00:49:21.799
Hey!

00:49:21.799 --> 00:49:24.299
Park Dal I!

00:49:24.299 --> 00:49:25.599
You, you...

00:49:25.599 --> 00:49:27.065
What are you doing?

00:49:27.065 --> 00:49:29.565
Mother, Father, why are you here?

00:49:31.832 --> 00:49:33.799
Royal Inspector.

00:49:33.799 --> 00:49:36.165
About that soup rice...

00:49:36.165 --> 00:49:38.265
- What? Hey!
- Let's take a rain check.

00:49:38.265 --> 00:49:39.865
I must go now.

00:49:39.865 --> 00:49:41.065
- What is she saying?
- Hide, hide.

00:49:41.065 --> 00:49:42.099
You want me to hide?

00:49:42.099 --> 00:49:44.065
Wait, we came all this way. Where are you going?

00:49:44.065 --> 00:49:46.899
And if we're taking a rain check,

00:49:46.899 --> 00:49:49.265
you should specify the new time clearly.

00:49:49.265 --> 00:49:50.699
Well then,

00:49:50.699 --> 00:49:53.899
[Oh Hour: 11 AM to 1 PM]
meet here tomorrow at noon.

00:49:53.899 --> 00:49:55.065
Oh hour?

00:49:55.065 --> 00:49:57.165
If I come at noon tomorrow, we'll meet here?

00:49:57.165 --> 00:49:58.499
- Yes.
- What?

00:49:58.499 --> 00:50:00.499
- What?
- I'll take my leave now.

00:50:00.499 --> 00:50:02.417
Why are you acting like this?

00:50:05.699 --> 00:50:07.765
She really has parents?

00:50:07.765 --> 00:50:10.665
Is there more you need to verify?

00:50:10.665 --> 00:50:11.765
No.

00:50:11.765 --> 00:50:15.232
If there's nothing else, don't meet her tomorrow.

00:50:15.232 --> 00:50:17.299
But Shin Won.

00:50:18.065 --> 00:50:20.865
It doesn't disappear when touched.

00:50:23.165 --> 00:50:26.232
That's why I keep wanting it.

00:50:27.032 --> 00:50:29.099
Can't I just be

00:50:29.765 --> 00:50:33.165
a little shameless, even for a moment?

00:50:40.932 --> 00:50:42.299
Where do you think you've come?

00:50:42.299 --> 00:50:43.632
This is Hanyang! Hanyang.

00:50:43.632 --> 00:50:44.932
The capital where the palace stands.

00:50:44.932 --> 00:50:46.465
Do you have any sense of that, or not?

00:50:46.465 --> 00:50:49.065
Mother, Father, if something
happens to you, what will I do alone?

00:50:49.065 --> 00:50:50.765
Good grief.

00:50:50.765 --> 00:50:52.432
Why is she stealing my lines?

00:50:52.432 --> 00:50:54.232
The one who made the mess is angry.

00:50:54.232 --> 00:50:56.599
And furious, at that.

00:50:56.599 --> 00:50:58.432
Like I wouldn't be mad right now?

00:50:58.432 --> 00:51:00.765
The eunuch and the head court lady
who had an affair and escaped as sinners

00:51:00.765 --> 00:51:03.599
boldly came all the way to Hanyang?

00:51:03.599 --> 00:51:04.732
How did you find that out?

00:51:04.732 --> 00:51:07.499
That we were head court lady
and eunuch? Did your aunt tell you?

00:51:07.499 --> 00:51:09.699
What are you saying?

00:51:09.699 --> 00:51:11.365
I'd be so dumb

00:51:11.365 --> 00:51:14.099
if I didn't notice what Father's like every day.

00:51:14.099 --> 00:51:18.532
Father's constantly trimming
and attaching his mustache day after day.

00:51:18.532 --> 00:51:19.599
And Mother?

00:51:19.599 --> 00:51:21.832
You are fluent in palace terms.

00:51:21.832 --> 00:51:23.199
It's obvious at first glance.

00:51:23.199 --> 00:51:25.532
The eunuch and head court lady

00:51:25.532 --> 00:51:28.165
had an affair and fled at night.

00:51:30.565 --> 00:51:32.865
Clever, see?

00:51:32.865 --> 00:51:36.365
My son, no, my daughter is so smart.

00:51:36.365 --> 00:51:39.232
Is this really something to applaud?

00:51:39.899 --> 00:51:41.699
It's something to be punished for.

00:51:41.699 --> 00:51:45.332
Right. Before real trouble comes,
you two pack and leave first.

00:51:45.332 --> 00:51:47.199
I have something to take care of before I go.

00:51:47.199 --> 00:51:48.365
Good grief.

00:51:48.365 --> 00:51:49.832
Where are you running off to?

00:51:49.832 --> 00:51:52.399
You think only we're criminals?
You're a criminal too.

00:51:52.399 --> 00:51:55.465
Want to get caught wandering around
and live as a slave forever?

00:51:55.465 --> 00:51:58.999
I've spent years erasing even the mole
on my nose to avoid being caught.

00:51:58.999 --> 00:52:00.599
There's always a way.

00:52:00.599 --> 00:52:02.199
Carefully hide just like this.

00:52:02.199 --> 00:52:04.565
Yeah, leave her be.

00:52:04.565 --> 00:52:08.199
Thinking her plain face
needs a pretty slave tattoo.

00:52:08.199 --> 00:52:10.465
Wow, how glamorous.

00:52:10.465 --> 00:52:12.099
What a character.

00:52:12.099 --> 00:52:13.665
Enough. Enough.

00:52:13.665 --> 00:52:16.699
When I leave, I'm no longer a person.

00:52:18.332 --> 00:52:19.365
What are you doing?

00:52:19.365 --> 00:52:21.199
- I'll just sleep.
- Yeah, right.

00:52:21.199 --> 00:52:23.832
- Sleep. Sleep.
- Go to sleep now.

00:52:43.732 --> 00:52:44.932
You wench!

00:52:44.932 --> 00:52:46.499
Going to the restroom, huh? Why?

00:52:46.499 --> 00:52:49.465
Court ladies have eyes but cannot see,

00:52:49.465 --> 00:52:52.499
mouths but cannot speak.

00:52:57.532 --> 00:52:59.365
Jeez.

00:53:07.832 --> 00:53:12.199
With the way you're acting,
how could I not know your backgrounds?

00:53:22.999 --> 00:53:25.432
Truly, thank you.

00:53:26.699 --> 00:53:27.732
Oh, my.

00:53:27.732 --> 00:53:29.499
I won't forget

00:53:29.499 --> 00:53:32.732
this favor even in death.

00:53:32.732 --> 00:53:34.899
Forget it.

00:53:35.599 --> 00:53:38.799
Leave all the bad memories behind

00:53:39.932 --> 00:53:42.832
and only build good ones.

00:54:05.065 --> 00:54:08.065
I'll just eat one bowl of soup
and come right back.

00:54:08.065 --> 00:54:12.065
Look at our daughter's audacity!

00:54:12.065 --> 00:54:15.532
Staking her life on a bowl of soup?

00:54:15.532 --> 00:54:17.365
Jeez.

00:54:21.832 --> 00:54:22.899
What is it?

00:54:22.899 --> 00:54:24.732
Here.

00:54:25.899 --> 00:54:27.732
My lord.

00:54:28.765 --> 00:54:33.199
If you're the merchant, the guild
and traders would know for sure.

00:54:33.199 --> 00:54:34.699
Do you even know Qing interpreters?

00:54:34.699 --> 00:54:37.065
I even did

00:54:37.065 --> 00:54:41.699
some business in Uiju,
Joseon's third city connecting

00:54:41.699 --> 00:54:43.165
Hanyang and Pyongyang.

00:54:43.165 --> 00:54:46.299
That's the hub for trade with Qing, isn't it?

00:54:47.365 --> 00:54:48.632
Can you find people too?

00:54:48.632 --> 00:54:49.932
Ugh,

00:54:49.932 --> 00:54:51.232
it's tiring to explain.

00:54:51.232 --> 00:54:53.732
Roaming around everywhere is my job.

00:54:53.732 --> 00:54:56.699
You can just imagine all the merchants I know

00:54:56.699 --> 00:54:59.299
being spread all over the country.

00:54:59.299 --> 00:55:00.999
I've found your use.

00:55:00.999 --> 00:55:02.999
We need to draw up a contract, so follow me.

00:55:02.999 --> 00:55:05.299
Can't. I have plans.

00:55:05.299 --> 00:55:08.299
I'm having rice soup with the secret inspector.

00:55:08.299 --> 00:55:12.532
- The inspector?
- Your cousin I met yesterday.

00:55:12.532 --> 00:55:14.465
He became a secret royal inspector already?

00:55:14.465 --> 00:55:18.199
Ah, so you're not very close.

00:55:19.232 --> 00:55:20.465
But

00:55:20.465 --> 00:55:25.332
how can a prince's cousin take an official post?

00:55:26.665 --> 00:55:28.499
That's...

00:55:29.632 --> 00:55:31.532
He's my maternal cousin.

00:55:33.099 --> 00:55:34.632
Ah, right.

00:55:34.632 --> 00:55:36.932
Makes sense.

00:55:36.932 --> 00:55:37.932
Alright.

00:55:37.932 --> 00:55:41.199
Anyway, come to my place after eating.

00:55:42.432 --> 00:55:45.132
Why would I go to a bachelor's house alone?

00:55:45.999 --> 00:55:47.832
Alone?

00:55:49.599 --> 00:55:51.699
Don't worry, I have many household members.

00:55:51.699 --> 00:55:54.299
Let's meet later then.

00:55:54.299 --> 00:55:56.299
Ask my cousin where my house is.

00:55:56.299 --> 00:55:58.465
And if you run away again,

00:55:58.465 --> 00:56:01.165
I'll report you to the Podocheong.

00:56:15.065 --> 00:56:17.699
Keep your eyes straight ahead when you walk.

00:56:18.832 --> 00:56:21.065
You should focus on your own path instead.

00:56:21.065 --> 00:56:22.465
- What?
- What?

00:56:22.465 --> 00:56:25.000
Hey you!

00:56:29.832 --> 00:56:33.265
Why is he losing his temper at me
after bumping into me?

00:56:37.165 --> 00:56:40.265
But, she said she'd come.
Why hasn't she arrived yet?

00:56:40.265 --> 00:56:42.199
Did something happen?

00:56:42.199 --> 00:56:45.165
I'm starving to death.

00:56:45.165 --> 00:56:48.599
Can I just eat first?

00:56:48.599 --> 00:56:50.465
Do you really think that's okay?

00:56:51.099 --> 00:56:53.299
Wait, you rented this entire tavern
for that backpack-carrying porter,

00:56:53.299 --> 00:56:55.099
yet you can't spare a single bowl of soup for me,

00:56:55.099 --> 00:56:58.699
who's served Your Highness all these years?

00:56:58.699 --> 00:56:59.699
Do you really think she's the same as you?

00:56:59.699 --> 00:57:00.832
What's the difference?

00:57:00.832 --> 00:57:02.365
The years I spent with Your Highness,

00:57:02.365 --> 00:57:04.265
my loyalty dedicated to you,

00:57:04.265 --> 00:57:06.899
how am I any less than that porter?

00:57:06.899 --> 00:57:09.899
My heart is different, you fool.

00:57:09.899 --> 00:57:11.899
Hmph.

00:57:13.999 --> 00:57:15.965
'Hmph'?

00:57:15.965 --> 00:57:17.965
You.

00:57:17.965 --> 00:57:19.832
Put some fire in your eyes

00:57:19.832 --> 00:57:21.632
and smile.

00:57:21.632 --> 00:57:24.232
Ugh, seriously.

00:57:26.532 --> 00:57:29.799
That guy's hopeless.

00:57:30.632 --> 00:57:33.999
The broth is rich.

00:57:54.165 --> 00:57:57.665
There's something familiar

00:57:57.665 --> 00:58:00.565
about this stranger.

00:58:01.299 --> 00:58:06.399
A scruffy little mustache on a smooth,

00:58:07.732 --> 00:58:12.032
unshaven chin, giving off

00:58:14.565 --> 00:58:17.965
a strangely timid vibe.

00:58:17.965 --> 00:58:19.565
A man,

00:58:19.565 --> 00:58:21.632
yet somehow

00:58:21.632 --> 00:58:25.041
not quite a man.

00:58:41.250 --> 00:58:43.275
[The First Place]

00:58:44.932 --> 00:58:46.165
No, no!

00:58:46.165 --> 00:58:48.965
Why are you dragging me around

00:58:48.965 --> 00:58:50.332
like some dog?

00:58:50.332 --> 00:58:52.899
You're insane! Insane.

00:58:52.899 --> 00:58:54.999
Isn't that the eunuch from earlier?

00:58:54.999 --> 00:58:57.732
Even you can tell, right? Huh?

00:58:57.732 --> 00:59:01.232
Wow, it's been a while since I came to Hanyang,

00:59:01.232 --> 00:59:02.699
and I've seen my juniors.

00:59:02.699 --> 00:59:06.165
Ah, so you like that?

00:59:06.165 --> 00:59:07.865
If a civil official is beside the eunuch,

00:59:07.865 --> 00:59:10.799
and a military official
beside the civil one, what could that be?

00:59:10.799 --> 00:59:13.965
Well, usually a king, a prince...

00:59:18.199 --> 00:59:22.132
- Or the Crown Prince.
- Shh.

00:59:22.132 --> 00:59:26.665
Come to think of it, wasn't the noble
with Dal I yesterday the Crown Prince?

00:59:26.665 --> 00:59:27.932
Wow.

00:59:27.932 --> 00:59:31.299
Your perception is just remarkable, really.

00:59:31.299 --> 00:59:33.099
So good!

00:59:34.099 --> 00:59:35.365
Jeez.

00:59:35.365 --> 00:59:37.199
With your utter lack of awareness,

00:59:37.199 --> 00:59:41.332
I'll have to watch out for you too.

00:59:41.332 --> 00:59:44.632
Anyway, where do we even find her?

00:59:44.632 --> 00:59:47.732
Though my body goes to Minister's house,

00:59:47.732 --> 00:59:50.600
my heart will always remain here.

00:59:52.899 --> 00:59:55.432
Did you handle the last task I gave you?

00:59:55.432 --> 00:59:56.799
Of course!

00:59:56.799 --> 00:59:59.089
That girl who ran off with the young lady

00:59:59.089 --> 01:00:01.299
won't remain safe.

01:00:11.399 --> 01:00:14.265
Walk straight and keep your eyes forward.

01:00:18.799 --> 01:00:20.599
Brother.

01:00:25.099 --> 01:00:29.832
People always leave a mess till the end.

01:00:29.832 --> 01:00:31.865
Hey, you thief!

01:00:31.865 --> 01:00:33.532
Catch her, catch her.

01:00:33.532 --> 01:00:35.599
Hey, you thief!

01:00:35.599 --> 01:00:36.832
Hey, you thief!

01:00:36.832 --> 01:00:38.965
You thief.

01:00:39.599 --> 01:00:43.032
Why are you doing this? Let go!

01:00:46.932 --> 01:00:48.465
How can a girl be so strong?

01:00:48.465 --> 01:00:51.232
Never underestimate a porter again.

01:00:51.999 --> 01:00:53.065
This is the girl.

01:00:53.065 --> 01:00:54.832
This rat stole my stuff.

01:00:54.832 --> 01:00:56.465
What nonsense is this now?

01:00:56.465 --> 01:00:58.065
Did you eat dog food for breakfast?

01:00:58.065 --> 01:00:59.865
You're putting real effort into barking lies.

01:00:59.865 --> 01:01:02.599
Let's see your belongings.

01:01:02.599 --> 01:01:04.999
What are you doing?

01:01:04.999 --> 01:01:06.499
I said it's nonsense!

01:01:06.499 --> 01:01:08.299
Look here.

01:01:13.632 --> 01:01:15.765
See? You're the thief.

01:01:15.765 --> 01:01:18.399
This trinket is the stolen item.

01:01:18.399 --> 01:01:19.865
Why would this suddenly...

01:01:19.865 --> 01:01:22.099
There's nothing more to see, take her away.

01:01:22.099 --> 01:01:23.332
- Yes.
- Yes.

01:01:23.332 --> 01:01:25.932
The slave hunters are still looking for you,

01:01:25.932 --> 01:01:29.132
so you must never go to Hanyang.

01:01:29.132 --> 01:01:31.099
Absolutely not.

01:01:31.099 --> 01:01:33.232
I must not go to Podocheong.

01:01:35.032 --> 01:01:36.565
Since I'm a merchant,

01:01:36.565 --> 01:01:40.599
[Dobang: Headquarters of the traveling merchants]
this must be handled according to dobang rules.

01:01:40.599 --> 01:01:41.899
Jangmunhyeong punishment?

01:01:41.899 --> 01:01:44.332
[Jangmunhyeong: Harsh punishment for the guilty]
Ugh, it'll be filled with screams.

01:01:44.332 --> 01:01:46.632
Indeed, cries will echo today.

01:01:46.632 --> 01:01:49.000
[Ethics Code: No lies, lust, misconduct, or theft]
We swore to avoid lies, lust,

01:01:49.000 --> 01:01:50.565
misconduct, and theft.

01:01:50.565 --> 01:01:53.099
Master Leader, that's not true.

01:01:53.099 --> 01:01:55.332
If I were guilty, I'd accept punishment,

01:01:55.332 --> 01:01:57.299
but I've never stolen anything.

01:01:57.299 --> 01:01:59.732
So, after getting a bit more clarity
on the details of the incident...

01:01:59.732 --> 01:02:00.765
Silence.

01:02:00.765 --> 01:02:03.099
Evidence was found blatantly in your belongings.

01:02:03.099 --> 01:02:04.599
How dare you try to deny it?

01:02:04.599 --> 01:02:06.132
- That wasn't...
- You there.

01:02:06.132 --> 01:02:07.665
Yes.

01:02:07.665 --> 01:02:12.499
After rolling up Park Dal I, who violated
the Ethics Code, beat her thirty times,

01:02:12.499 --> 01:02:14.932
then sever the lower leg.

01:02:15.865 --> 01:02:17.732
Leg amputation is ordered.

01:02:17.732 --> 01:02:19.832
- Yes.
- Yes.

01:02:19.832 --> 01:02:21.032
Leg amputation?

01:02:21.032 --> 01:02:24.399
[Leg Amputation: Cripple limbs with roof tiles]
Master Leader, I'm truly wronged.

01:02:24.399 --> 01:02:25.432
Enough.

01:02:25.432 --> 01:02:27.799
Oh, my goodness.

01:02:27.799 --> 01:02:30.265
No leg amputation. I beg you.

01:02:30.265 --> 01:02:31.399
Beat her harshly.

01:02:31.399 --> 01:02:33.199
- Yes.
- Yes.

01:02:55.399 --> 01:02:57.299
Stop.

01:03:01.665 --> 01:03:08.032
 You flew in like a cloud 

01:03:10.465 --> 01:03:16.632
 Departing like starlight, my beloved 

01:03:19.132 --> 01:03:27.699
 Oh, will my love return to me 

01:03:27.699 --> 01:03:36.832
 Oh, how futile all becomes 

01:03:37.832 --> 01:03:40.999
 All but a dream 

01:03:46.332 --> 01:03:48.465
What is this madness?

01:03:48.465 --> 01:03:50.232
It's Jangmunhyeong punishment in progress.

01:03:50.232 --> 01:03:54.599
No nobleman can stop the Jangmunhyeong punishment.

01:03:56.499 --> 01:04:04.299
 Even the wind sings your song 

01:04:05.299 --> 01:04:09.932
 Oh, will my love return to me 

01:04:09.932 --> 01:04:12.365
Then I'll show you

01:04:13.899 --> 01:04:15.465
that I'm the exception.

01:04:15.465 --> 01:04:22.532
 Oh, how futile all becomes 

01:04:22.532 --> 01:04:26.899
 Born of dreams, living and dying in dreams 

01:04:26.899 --> 01:04:31.299
 It's all for naught 

01:04:31.299 --> 01:04:40.369
 What use is dreaming such dreams 

01:04:50.632 --> 01:04:54.965
How did you come here, my lord?

01:04:54.965 --> 01:04:57.297
Didn't we have plans?

01:05:07.165 --> 01:05:08.999
Let's go

01:05:08.999 --> 01:05:10.299
eat some rice soup.

01:05:10.299 --> 01:05:15.232
 Oh, will my love return to me 

01:05:15.232 --> 01:05:24.665
 Oh, how futile all becomes 

01:05:25.532 --> 01:05:28.832
 All but a dream 

01:06:00.565 --> 01:06:02.265
Take this road and leave Hanyang immediately.

01:06:02.265 --> 01:06:04.799
You, a lowly person,
must pay for that face you have.

01:06:04.799 --> 01:06:06.632
Why should I obey you?

01:06:06.632 --> 01:06:08.399
Where are you going?

01:06:08.399 --> 01:06:09.565
To propose.

01:06:09.565 --> 01:06:10.965
Didn't you promise?

01:06:10.965 --> 01:06:13.899
Are you speaking of rebellion now?

01:06:13.899 --> 01:06:17.532
So make your decision.

01:06:17.532 --> 01:06:20.765
Brother, do you trust me?

01:06:20.765 --> 01:06:22.232
I do.

01:06:22.232 --> 01:06:24.665
Because you're family.